data.name: Red
data.description: Creative entrees combined with the highest quality ingredients in a warm, modern environment are the hallmarks of RED, downtown Madison’s premier sushi restaurant. Traditional menu items are executed with painstaking precision, keeping the focus on the beauty and fresh flavors of the fish. We take a creative approach in forging our signature rolls, resulting in inspired combinations of flavor.

data.name: Dotty Dumpling's Dowry

photo.caption: Famous Melting Pot burger and Wisconsin cheese curds

data.description: Dotty Dumpling's Dowry is a Madison institution favored by the locals for over 40 years. Located in the heart of downtown, Dotty's offers award winning hamburgers, Friday fish fry, homemade soups and chili, fresh salads and so much more! Cozy up in a booth or at the bar and pick from 24 Wisconsin craft beers on tap while enjoying some Blues or Motown music in the back round. Dotty's is a Madison tradition enjoyed by guests of all ages!

data.name: Ian's Pizza on State
data.description: Ian's Pizza specializes in pizza by the slice. Our claim to fame is mastering the recipe for Mac n' Cheese Pizza. We have around two dozen different varieties of pizza ranging from Smoked Brisket and Tots to Spinach Feta Pesto. We have a team of food "masterminds" that showcase our new recipes in our weekly special slices and seasonal slices. We only serve top quality food and continue to push the boundaries of culinary exploration. At Ian's Pizza on State we also work closely with local farmers and the farmers market to offer one of the best and unique salad stations around. Almost everything we offer is prepped fresh daily in store including several delicious salad dressings.

data.ranking: #1 of 6 Specialty Food Market in Madison
data.description: Fromagination is an artisan cheese shop, with local specialty foods, on the Capitol Square in Madison, Wisconsin. It carries a variety of Wisconsin artisan cheeses, along with some U.S. and international cheeses. It serves sandwiches and salads for lunch; and specializes in gift sets for the holidays and other special occasions. It also carries cakes of cheese for weddings or other events.
